  "1812910": {
    "name": "Great Houses of Calderia",
    "steam_appid": 1812910,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/88fd47ede46ac6a6386bd3c680919eba.poster.avif?t=1758889157\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/88fd47ede46ac6a6386bd3c680919eba.webm?t=1758889157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/88fd47ede46ac6a6386bd3c680919eba.mp4?t=1758889157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/57fcc9c7362bee88456654876ccfa3a1.avif?t=1758889157\" width=616 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《卡尔德里亚大家族》这款大型封建战略游戏起发自地中海文艺复兴。你将扮演贵族家族，目标是统治卡尔德里亚，这个古老的帝国省份因为众人争权夺势而饱受摧残。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让你的家族变得伟大，扩大影响力并战胜敌人，在卡尔德里亚一路崛起，并夺得渴求权力的总督宝座！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/8a5540a7cc05cbc51c2d2a1657018348.webp?t=1758889157\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不只操控着领袖，也必须管理家族中的成员，就像昔日的领袖那样！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理你的家族领袖以及底下那些不守规矩的家族成员，每个角色都有自己的故事和欲望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指派家族成员执行重要任务并管理他们的时间，无论他们是否喜欢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在指派任务时，需要考粮道角色的特性和个性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色的个性和特性会随着他们经历不同的事件而有所变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/c749b93bbc48a5ecc527a4193d1c200e.poster.avif?t=1758889157\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/c749b93bbc48a5ecc527a4193d1c200e.webm?t=1758889157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/c749b93bbc48a5ecc527a4193d1c200e.mp4?t=1758889157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/aa55754350a42cca43517286d08e4c8f.avif?t=1758889157\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗和重要外交事件中做出重要决定，包括：联姻、和平谈判、封官加爵，借此斩获优势制霸对手</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过实时战术单位管理系统主导战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光是战斗还不足以获得新头衔，你还需要在外交关系、狡诈权谋和繁荣交易这三者之间取得微妙的平衡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/7b733d03dba40876098d4dab46cc6661.poster.avif?t=1758889157\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/7b733d03dba40876098d4dab46cc6661.webm?t=1758889157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/7b733d03dba40876098d4dab46cc6661.mp4?t=1758889157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/1d303b03f5d38877ce8ade9addcaf700.webp?t=1758889157\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索卡尔德里亚的奇幻土地，挖掘其中的传奇和秘辛，你的所作所为将影响故事，并开创出不同的剧情走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为你的家族定义传统、价值观和目标。可能性无穷无尽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在家族规模扩大后，体验角色的个人故事，并不断斩获更崇高的名望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/6c799d9aad035e1a983a958972581155.poster.avif?t=1758889157\" width=610 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/6c799d9aad035e1a983a958972581155.webm?t=1758889157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/6c799d9aad035e1a983a958972581155.mp4?t=1758889157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >围了确保你的家族经受得起时间的考验，并且能在卡尔德里亚一路崛起，你必须：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理并拓展你自己的封地及子民。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提高自己的贵族地位并册封其他人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为你的氏族发展丰富多元的传统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得荣誉头衔，这将决定你的统治如何影响卡尔德利亚的最终命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812910/extras/76f4cd0aeaea1fffa6fd0418f1e69be1.avif?t=1758889157\" width=615 height=114 /></span></p>",
